videos.description: Kennedy McKoy finds the end zone to put the Mountaineers in front.
videos.headline: McKoy puts West Virginia ahead of Kansas

videos.description: Justin Crawford takes it in from 11 yards for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Crawford tacks onto lead for Mountaineers

videos.description: Kennedy McKoy finds an open hole and scores a 23-yard TD for West Virginia.
videos.headline: McKoy gets in the end zone for the 2nd time

videos.description: Khalil Herbert responds for the Jayhawks with a long touchdown run.
videos.headline: Herbert uses speed to break open for 67-yard TD

videos.description: Khalil Herbert is too fast for the Mountaineer defense as he breaks open a 60-yard run that leads to a short touchdown run on the next play.
videos.headline: Herbert scores TD after huge run

videos.description: Taylor Martin pulls Kansas within a touchdown after a one-yard run.
videos.headline: Martin makes it a one score game

videos.description: Will Grier finds David Sills V for the second touchdown of the day to extend the Mountaineer lead over Jayhawks.
videos.headline: Sills pulls down 2nd TD grab

videos.description: Peyton Bender tosses it to Steven Sims Jr. for the touchdown to keep the Jayhawks in the game.
videos.headline: Sims keeps Kansas alive with TD grab

videos.description: Will Grier makes it a two-score game for West Virginia.
videos.headline: Grier keeps it for 3-yard TD run

videos.description: Mike Couzens and John Congemi break down the Mountaineer 56-34 victory over the Jayhawks.
videos.headline: West Virginia wins in shootout over Kansas.
